rawContent:
Compositionality, an important aspect of language, in Singlish:

“kiaxi”: fear of death =
“Scared coronavirus.”

“kiasu”: fear of losing out =
“Better buy up masks and rice before others hoard.”

“Remdesivir works. But supply limited. I better fall ill first” = “kiasi also kiasu”
